  13:main.c        ****  *
  14:main.c        ****  * ========================================
  15:main.c        ****  *
  16:main.c        ****  * Uses HamflyAPI (hamfly.h) for all gimbal communication.
  17:main.c        ****  *
  18:main.c        ****  * Modes:
  19:main.c        ****  *   STANDBY   passive; pump runs; 1 Hz status if telemetry valid.
  20:main.c        ****  *             Set boresight origin here before entering other modes.
  21:main.c        ****  *   JOYSTICK  10 Hz QX277 TX.  Joystick (rate) and numpad presets
  22:main.c        ****  *             share the mode — preset executes, settles to within
  23:main.c        ****  *             PRESET_SETTLE_DEG of target (or PRESET_SETTLE_MS
  24:main.c        ****  *             timeout), then joystick resumes automatically.
  25:main.c        ****  *   NUDGE     keyboard-driven absolute accumulation for beam-profiler
  26:main.c        ****  *             calibration.  Each keypress adds a fixed step to the
  27:main.c        ****  *             accumulated pan/tilt target, clamped to software limits.
  28:main.c        ****  *             Current accumulated position prints after every step.
  29:main.c        ****  *             No joystick input in this mode.
  30:main.c        ****  *
  31:main.c        ****  *   t  exit to STANDBY     
  32:main.c        ****  *   x  kill + exit
  33:main.c        ****  */
  34:main.c        **** 
